  "description": "A breathtaking nighttime view of a cityscape illuminated with vibrant lights, featuring a fireworks display over the harbor. A long bridge stretches across the dark water, adorned with glowing lights that create a beautiful reflection. The city skyline is a mix of tall buildings, some with distinct architectural designs, and a backdrop of hills shrouded in shadow. The fireworks explode in bursts of white and gold, adding a celebratory touch to the scene. The overall impression is one of grandeur and festivity.",
